Wood elf smiths have a pretty sweet deal now...<p>

(Karana) Imbued Mithril Fier'dal morning star<br>
1HB damage 9, delay 35<br>
WIS +2, DEX +2, AGI +4<br>
Usable by followers of Karana Only<br>
Player Made<p>

This thing requires about 25 Plat in components (with good cha) and sells for 200 PP on most servers  Trivials at over 175 too.<p>

There is a Tunare version as well that adds to CHA rather than DEX but it requires an imbued emerald so its a bit more expensive. <p>

They both require Imbued gems but the Plains pebbles are foraged and buying a stack of imbued ones should be pretty economical. They also require morning dew as a temper  but that easily foraged in G Fay and Lesser Fay</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
