<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Iksars have the best smithing city and the Enchanted Cabilis scale armor is some of the best in the game. Look at the cape.<p>

AC12 +4str +2wis wt3.0<p>

This "smithed" item has only a couple of capes in the game that are better but they are no drop or sell for 20k pp. Best I can figure this cape should sell for about 6k pp. Not bad for a smithed item. I have made 15 sets of Regular Cabilis Scale armor to date and each sold for 1k pp so smithing has been very profitable for me and I look forward to it being even more so in the future.<p>

